ing: 1 (8 ounce) package PHILADELPHIA Cream Cheese, softened
2 cups thawed COOL WHIP Whipped Topping
1/4 cup hot fudge ice cream topping, warmed
n: Peanut Butter and Fudge Swirl Pie
des: "Fudge sauce is swirled through a pie filling of cream cheese, peanut butter and whipped topping in this easy and luscious, no-bake dessert."
ins:
Beat cream cheese, sugar and peanut butter in large bowl with mixer until blended. Gently stir in COOL WHIP.
Spoon into crust; drizzle with fudge topping. Swirl gently with knife.
Refrigerate 4 hours or until firm. Refrigerate leftovers.
